WEBVTT

00:05:29.339 --> 00:05:33.307
cited Facebook because the ad tools
allowed discrimination in housing,

00:05:33.331 --> 00:05:35.158
in violation of the Fair Housing Act.

00:05:35.182 --> 00:05:36.673
And immediately after that,

00:05:36.697 --> 00:05:38.837
we heard that our
intelligence agencies said

00:05:38.861 --> 00:05:41.403
the Russians were trying
to interfere in the election.

00:05:41.427 --> 00:05:43.578
That is when I reached out
to Mark and Sheryl,

00:05:43.602 --> 00:05:45.591
at the end of October of 2016.

00:05:45.615 --> 00:05:47.529
CA: The thing that's puzzling about this

00:05:47.553 --> 00:05:49.338
is what to make of why this happened.

00:05:49.362 --> 00:05:53.355
I mean, one view would be
that Facebook were excited

00:05:53.379 --> 00:05:56.553
to let their platform be used in this way

00:05:56.577 --> 00:05:58.394
because they made a fortune from it.

00:05:58.418 --> 00:06:01.593
When you actually look at the numbers,
if that was their intention,